This paper deals with image stylization, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and computer graphics (cs.GR). The paper also mentions the use of machine learning techniques to learn style ranking, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper proposes a novel technique for transferring global color and tone, which could be considered a sub-topic of multimedia (cs.MM).
